      right: ["Anaphylaxis: hypotension, laryngeal edema, bronchospasm", "Transfusion reaction: fever, flank pain, dark urine", "Lupus nephritis: proteinuria, low complement", "Poison ivy: vesicular dermatitis at contact site", "PPD: induration ≥10 mm at 48-72 hours"]
